doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='At Codeline1, the first line of code sparks innovation. Join us for cutting-edge software solutions that elevate your vision.')
        meta(name='author', content='Codeline1')

        title Codeline1 - Software Development

        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')

        // Bootstrap icons
        link(href='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.5.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css', rel='stylesheet')

        // Google fonts
        link(rel='preconnect', href='https://fonts.gstatic.com')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Newsreader:ital,wght@0,600;1,600&display=swap', rel='stylesheet')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Mulish:ital,wght@0,300;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,300;1,500;1,600;1,700&display=swap', rel='stylesheet')
        link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Kanit:ital,wght@0,400;1,400&display=swap', rel='stylesheet')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body#page-top

        // Navigation
        nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-light.fixed-top.shadow-sm
            .container.px-sm-5.px-3
                a.navbar-brand.fw-bold(href='#page-top') 
                    img(src='assets/img/codeline1-logo.svg', alt='codeline1 logo', height='35px')
                button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    | Menu
                    i.bi-list
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.ms-auto.me-4.my-3.my-lg-0
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.me-lg-3(href='#features') Services
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.me-lg-3(href='#download') About us
                    button.btn.btn-primary.rounded-pill.px-3.mb-2.mb-lg-0(data-bs-toggle='modal', data-bs-target='#feedbackModal')
                        span.d-flex.align-items-center
                            i.bi-chat-text-fill.me-2
                            span.small Talk to us

        // Mashead header
        header.masthead
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                    .col-lg-6
                        // Mashead text and app badges
                        .mb-5.mb-lg-0.text-center.text-lg-start
                            h1.display-1.lh-1.mb-3.hero-heading
                                | Your 
                                br
                                span#productHeroHeading 
                                br
                                | Our 
                                br
                                span#codeHeroHeading Code.
                            p.lead.fw-normal.text-muted.mb-5 At Codeline1, the first line of code sparks innovation. Join us for cutting-edge software solutions that elevate your vision.

        // Quote/testimonial aside
        aside.text-center.bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.justify-content-center
                    .col-xl-8
                        .h2.fs-1.text-white Our main goal is to deliver software that adds real value to each client.

        // App features section
        section#features
            video#video(muted='muted', autoplay='', loop='', style='max-width: 100%; height: 100%;')
                source(src='assets/img/animation.mp4', type='video/mp4')
            .container.px-5.features-cards
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center
                    .col-xxl-8.order-lg-1.mb-5.mb-lg-0
                        .container-fluid.px-5
                            .row.gx-5
                                .col-md-6.mb-5
                                    // Feature item
                                    .text-center
                                        i.bi-code-slash.icon-feature.text-gradient.d-block.mb-3
                                        h3.font-alt Software Development
                                        p.text-muted.mb-0 Solutions for a wide range of platforms, including mobile, desktop, web and cloud-based applications.
                                .col-md-6.mb-5
                                    // Feature item
                                    .text-center
                                        i.bi-people.icon-feature.text-gradient.d-block.mb-3
                                        h3.font-alt Technical Consulting
                                        p.text-muted.mb-0 Are you facing challenges in your software development or deployment proccess? We can help.
                            .row
                                .col-md-6.mb-5.mb-md-0
                                    // Feature item
                                    .text-center
                                        i.bi-lightbulb.icon-feature.text-gradient.d-block.mb-3
                                        h3.font-alt Digital Transformation
                                        p.text-muted.mb-0 We help businesses find and develop ways to improve their processes and cut costs using technology.
                                .col-md-6
                                    // Feature item
                                    .text-center
                                        i.bi-patch-check.icon-feature.text-gradient.d-block.mb-3
                                        h3.font-alt In-house solutions
                                        p.text-muted.mb-0 We have a variety of white labeled softwares that might meet your needs, this is a cheap and quick option to enter the market.
                    .col-lg-4.order-lg-0
                        // Features section device mockup

        // Basic features section
        section.bg-light
            .container.px-5
                .row.gx-5.align-items-center.justify-content-center.justify-content-lg-between
                    .col-12.col-lg-5
                        h2.display-4.lh-1.mb-4 About us
                        p.lead.fw-normal.text-muted.mb-5.mb-lg-0 
                        | Codeline1 is an initiative created and maintained by software developers from Brazil 
                        | who have seen many problems in the software development model used during their careers, 
                        | from small companies to large enterprises.
                        p
                        | Our goal is to deliver value to the client in the way that is most profitable for them rather 
                        | than taking the path that is most profitable for us.
                        p
                        | All software built by Codeline1 uses a client-centered approach, we believe that the developer 
                        | should be the person who knows the most about the business after the company's senior management.
                        p 
                        | We don't want to stay just in the software, we want to help your business succeed!
                    .col-sm-8.col-md-6
                        .px-5.px-sm-0
                            img.img-fluid.rounded-circle(src='/assets/img/group.jpg', alt='...')

        // Call to action section
        section.cta
            .cta-content
                .container.px-5
                    h2.text-white.display-1.lh-1.mb-4
                        | Stop waiting.
                        br
                        | Start building.

        // App badge section
        section#download.bg-gradient-primary-to-secondary
            .container.px-5
                h2.text-center.text-white.font-alt.mb-4 Under Construction!
                .d-flex.flex-column.flex-lg-row.align-items-center.justify-content-center
                    //- a.me-lg-3.mb-4.mb-lg-0(href='#!')
                    //-     img.app-badge(src='assets/img/google-play-badge.svg', alt='...')
                    //- a(href='#!')
                    //-     img.app-badge(src='assets/img/app-store-badge.svg', alt='...')

        // Footer
        footer.bg-black.text-center.py-5
            .container.px-5
                .text-white-50.small
                    .mb-2 &copy; Codeline1 2024. All Rights Reserved.
        
        include includes/feedback-modal.pug

        // Bootstrap core JS
        script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')

        // Core theme JS
        script(src='js/scripts.js')

        script(src='https://cdn.startbootstrap.com/sb-forms-latest.js')
